## Project

SWGEmu-based Pre-CU server **SWG Bellum Gero** — tailored gameplay, custom content, lore-appropriate design.

- **Engine**: engine3 (git submodule at `utils/engine3/`)
- **Build**: CMake + Ninja
- **Language**: C++17, Lua 5.3
- **Database**: MariaDB (`swgemu` database)
- **Object Store**: Berkeley DB 5.3
- **Platform**: Linux (WSL2 Debian on Windows 11)

---

## Core Behavior

- **Lua first:** Add items/NPCs/stats/spawns/loot/conversations/quests via Lua scripts before touching C++. C++ only when impossible in Lua.
- **Shadow PC:** Code and asset editing only. No build/run/test. No WSL commands.
- **Build/test/run:** WSL machines only (Main Desktop or Laptop).
- **TRE files:** Both WSL machines access TREs at `/mnt/c/BellumGero`. Read-only — do not modify.

