## Build System

### Commands

```bash
# Standard debug build
make build-ninja-debug NINJAFLAGS="-j6"   # Main Desktop (64 GB RAM, 6 cores)
make build-ninja-debug NINJAFLAGS="-j4"   # Laptop (16 GB RAM)

# Clean build
rm -rf build/unix/ninja-debug && make build-ninja-debug NINJAFLAGS="-j4"
```

### Known Build Fixes

| Issue | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| WSL2 OOM kills build | Use `-j4` (Laptop) or `-j6` (Main Desktop); ensure `.wslconfig` is applied |
| `redundant move` errors | Remove `std::move()` from return statements (GCC 14 treats as error) |
| `crctable` duplicate symbol | Add `add_link_options(-Wl,--allow-multiple-definition)` to CMakeLists.txt |
| Discord `#ifdef` missing | Wrap `handleDiscordReady/Error` in `#ifdef WITH_DISCORD_INTEGRATION` with `#else` stubs |

### WSL2 Config (`.wslconfig`)

**Laptop** (`C:\Users\Mobile-Wookie\.wslconfig`):
