## Running the Server (WSL only)

```bash
sudo systemctl start mariadb
cd MMOCoreORB/bin && ./core3
```

### Expected Startup Sequence
1. Config loaded
2. TRE files scanned (`.exe`/`.dll` errors are harmless on Linux)
3. Templates loaded
4. Database connected
5. Zones initialized
6. `READY` — server accepting connections

### Non-Fatal Startup Errors

| Error | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| `Invalid path: tre.exe` | None needed — harmless on Linux |
| `Did not find conf/config-local.lua` | `touch bin/conf/config-local.lua` |
| `Failed to load ad queue file` | `touch bin/custom_scripts/ad_queue.lua` |

